## Notes

* Using SPNEGO with MIT is able to use the Kerberos mech without having to install anything else
* Defaults to Kerberos (sole mech)
* The 1st token contains the SPNEGO token which includes just the KRB5 mechs and the first Kerberos token
* The 2nd token contains the SPNEGO response wrapping the Kerberos response stating the accepted mech and no MIC
